# 📈 Stock Price Prediction using Machine Learning

## 🚀 Project Overview
This project focuses on predicting stock prices using Machine Learning techniques. It uses historical stock market data to analyze trends and forecast future prices.

Stock price prediction is a challenging task due to the dynamic nature of financial markets, where multiple factors influence price movement. :contentReference[oaicite:0]{index=0}

---

## 📂 Dataset
- Historical stock price data (Open, High, Low, Close, Volume)
- Time-series based dataset
- Data collected from financial sources (e.g., Yahoo Finance / CSV dataset)

---

